Author: Lunaseki
Text: Yeahhhh... you aren’t alone. I want to not starve myself, I want to eat normal, but every. Damn. Time. I end up overeating. And I’d rather be skinny and miserable than fat and miserable. Whether it’s binge eating or restricting, it’s like there’s no way out sometimes.   I do hope it gets better for you though. I’ve noticed I’m at my happiest/most content when I just practice self love and care. It can be really hard to manage when you have depression too LOL but it’s worth trying
